newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 2,060 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 2,060 contracts.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 2,060 contracts compared with 3,496 overnight Monday.
There were 82 wheat, 1,373 corn, 451 soybean, 27 soymeal, 27 soyoil, 11 oat, 54 corn calls, 33 corn puts and two soybean puts traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 3/4 cent higher to 1/2 cent lower, corn was 2-3/4 cents higher to 1/4 cent lower and soybeans were 1/4 to 7-1/4 cents higher.
